@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "API Express\n(server + router + controller)" as API
component "CartService" as SERVICE
interface "IStorage" as ISTORAGE
component "InMemory" as MEM
component "PostgresStorage" as PGSTORAGE
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

API --> SERVICE
SERVICE --> ISTORAGE
MEM ..|> ISTORAGE
PGSTORAGE ..|> ISTORAGE
PGSTORAGE --> DB

note right of API
Au demarrage, le server choisit
le driver via STORAGE_DRIVER.
end note

note bottom of SERVICE
Le metier depend du port IStorage,
pas de Postgres directement.
end note
@enduml
